org.apache.poi.hssf.record

Class EmbeddedObjectRefSubRecord

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.poi.hssf.record.SubRecord
      • org.apache.poi.hssf.record.EmbeddedObjectRefSubRecord
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Duplicatable, GenericRecord 

    public final class EmbeddedObjectRefSubRecord
extends SubRecord
    ftPictFmla (0x0009)

    A sub-record within the OBJ record which stores a reference to an object stored in a separate entry within the OLE2 compound file.

    (ftPictFMla（0x 0009）BOJ记录中的子记录，其中存储对存储在MBE 2复合文件内单独条目中的对象的引用。)

        getDataSize in class SubRecord(SubRecord类中的getDataSize)
        Returns:
        the size of the data for this record (which is always 4 bytes less than the total record size). Note however, that ushort encoded after the record sid is usually but not always the data size.(此记录的数据大小（始终比总记录大小小4个字节）。不过请注意，记录sid之后编码的ushort通常是但不总是数据大小。)

      • getStreamId

        public java.lang.Integer getStreamId()
        Gets the stream ID containing the actual data. The data itself can be found under a top-level directory entry in the OLE2 filesystem under the name "MBDxxxxxxxx" where xxxxxxxx is this ID converted into hex (in big endian order, funnily enough.)(获取包含实际数据的流ID。数据本身可以在MBE 2文件系统中名为“MBDxxxxxxxx”的顶级目录项下找到，其中xxxxxxxx是转换为十六进制的ID（以大序顺序，很有趣。）)
        Returns:
        the data stream ID. Possibly null(数据流ID。可能为空)
